{"tid":267364,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE雞注意啦！有個學界電競大伏等緊你！","createTime":"2017-06-02T08:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T09:16:28.000Z","uid":13685,"like":5,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f66c8e21745e02fd3d0a2a7bc64ff0251067db9","tid":267364,"uid":13685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T08:42:42.000Z","msg":"見近排咁多HKXE Comxpass既post<br />\n好似好少人提果間惠理VE 呢間野分分鐘伏過其他學店。<br />\n<br />\n上年我個friend考完DSE之後不停俾惠理啲人打嚟洗腦<br />\n個friend去到讀仲同我講話好好<br />\n個校長又俾佢地組籃球隊又拎一大舊錢俾佢地做生意<br />\n我都已經覺得有問題<br />\n正常你話搞下年宵都ok<br />\n俾班學生自己做生意我真係R晒頭<br />\n去到後尾先知原來係用呢個方法綁住啲學生唔俾佢走<br />\n如果參加咗嘅一有退學嘅諗法就會叫晒全部其他同學一齊洗腦講到自己幾熱血<br />\n話一齊衝仲逼你簽份野話如果走嘅要賠幾多錢<br />\n利申:我朋友唔係我<br />\n<br />\n近排見佢地同咩築夢電競合作<br />\n一有post就秒分享 都唔知係咪有親<br />\n依家借D而搞個淨係for中學生嘅比賽<br />\n本身都冇咩問題 點知佢就對DSE既想參加既學生特别多要求<br />\n寫到明今日DSE既話一定要話全日制學校 仲話幫手同學校方面傾<br />\n為咗呃人可以去到幾盡？<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zRMcTIn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzRMcTIn.jpg&h=a2ffcc0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/8AuYREJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8AuYREJ.jpg&h=451389db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/R43dJcP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FR43dJcP.png&h=d5f6183d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad2f7766a92d86d7250ca492cf033ec6380e6b72","tid":267364,"uid":35637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T08:45:31.000Z","msg":"見到都覺得伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd877c2660b712e65e73c199c7c8c4c814466b9e","tid":267364,"uid":41742,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T08:47:02.000Z","msg":"打機學校?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6145552699584908bc412c1fe0ae4a35058a9d","tid":267364,"uid":71712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T08:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249421be971296749a2c576669008d43321377ec","tid":267364,"uid":96983,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T08:56:10.000Z","msg":"所以話毒撚既錢真係好易呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b67afde8d5ab19b7478d2bf454d3077b7040778","tid":267364,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T08:59:06.000Z","msg":"ON9, <br />\n幾時有屌競"},{"pid":"e7bc2bd986f7966cd9c74d4f39b00db8ccc2d3e0","tid":267364,"uid":13685,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T09:34:40.000Z","msg":"推比多D人見到<br />\n叫自己D細佬妹小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49425abba9feafeced8caccbaa09492311764e7f","tid":267364,"uid":52472,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T09:53:14.000Z","msg":"不推不是人"},{"pid":"5bb5c3896043f8a27ddbb7f4411028a685afc738","tid":267364,"uid":78374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:13:29.000Z","msg":"我記得之前TVB有節目介紹過一間香港打機學校<br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪呢間  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3895e1455651b9527339b3cb88c6e70c4d1d0aa","tid":267364,"uid":119828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T06:27:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我記得之前TVB有節目介紹過一間香港打機學校<br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪呢間  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該唔係<br />\n<br />\n由「圍威喂」打機變成一項運動產業，電競需要大量人才。20歲出頭的方俊謙（底線）及朱仲賢（朱仔），過去分別為電競賽評及寫手，大半年前獲天使基金成立「電子競技學院」，為本地首間開宗明義的「打機學校」，為有志投身行業者提供方向。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170322/56461189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170322%2F56461189&d=1PqeU65tlB6pUrEWQ1zVbTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=42d931b6\" data-ef-url=\"http